article_text:
Donna Fourtner, Cañon City, will marry Kyle Middleton of Buffalo, Minn., on July 19. (Courtesy Photo)

Mr. and Mrs. Marty and Amy Fourtner of Cañon City announce the engagement of their daughter, Donna Fourtner, also of Cañon City, to Kyle Middleton of Buffalo, Minn., son of Kurt and Carmelita Zweifel of Buffalo.

The wedding will be July 19, 2014, at Evangelical Free Church of Cañon City.

The bride-to-be recently completed her masters degree in Organization Development from Friends University in Wichita, Kan. The groom is a High School Chemistry teacher and tennis coach at Pueblo West High School.
